info.title: SDC Form Filler
info.description:
This profile defines the expected capabilities of the ''SDC Form Filler'' role when conforming to the S&I Framework's [[index|Structured Data Capture FHIR implementation guide]]. This role is responsible for retrieving pre-defined forms, requesting pre-population of forms and/or auto-populating forms, guiding the user through verifying populated data and submitting completed or partially-completed forms.
Note that Form Fillers may also take on the role of [[sdc-form-archiver|Form Archiver]] if they have a requirement to retain the completed version of a form (and potentially the source data that was used to complete it).
